-- Axis Hires Pesce for Surety Business, Reporting to Zarandona
-- B y   M e g a n   H i c k e y
-- 2013-07-01T21:00:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-01/axis-hires-pesce-for-surety-business-reporting-to-zarandona.html
Axis Capital Holdings Ltd. (AXS)  hired
David Pesce of  WR Berkley Corp. (WRB)  as director of surety, reporting
to Richard Zarandona, head of the unit that handles deals with
contractors.  Pesce will be based in Berkeley Heights, New Jersey,
according to a Business Wire statement today from Bermuda-based
Axis.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Megan Hickey in New York at 
